A/76/207. Indigenous Peoples and toxics;
A/77/183. mercury, small-scale gold mining and human rights;
A/HRC/51/35. detoxification and decarbonization, and the need for integrated solutions;
A/HRC/54/25. shipping, toxics and human rights;
A/HRC/54/25/Add.2. human rights issues relating to all business enterprises, both transnational and other, regarding the environmentally sound management and disposal of hazardous substances and wastes; and the human right to a safe, clean, healthy, sustainable and non‑toxic environment,
